1.0.name: wordpress/rss-campaign
1.0.description: This Plugin adds the option to track your RSS reader or Twitter clicks by using Campaigns. You can use Google Analytics and/or Piwik. Twitter Campagns can shorten by Bit.ly And now you can add a QR-Code to Facebook liked Pages.
